{center}
{subhead}IOSPIRIT: VHI Studio 6.0 available{def}
{left}
{pp}
(16/12/02)
{pp}
While VHI Studio 6.0 already was available at the Amiga+Retro Computing 2002,
it is now also regularly available as download- and package-version. Furthermore, you
can now order an update from version 4.x/5.x and VLRec (NG).
{pp}
New features since the last version include support for AmithlonTV by Guido Mersmann
 and a filesystem-driver specialised in USB-cardreaders (under Poseidon).
{pp}
Customers buying version 6.0 will get free access to all future 6.x versions via Internet.
{pp}
Size of download is 2.35Mb from http://www.iospirit.de
{pp}
Features:
{pp}
* Video capture to disk{p}
* Still image grab to disk{p}
* Picture download from supported cameras{p}
* Webcam with FTP to your web site{p}
* Timelapse animation{p}
* Preview with upto 9 channels{p}
* Watch TV on your Workbench{p}
* Models for different OS' and CPUs{p}
* Integration with fxPaint
{pp}
Cost from EUR 36.99 (download) to 39.99 (package)
{pp}